'''ᱡᱷᱟᱨᱤᱭᱟ''' [[ᱡᱷᱟᱨᱠᱷᱚᱸᱰ]] ᱯᱚᱱᱚᱛ, [[ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ]] ᱨᱮ [[ᱫᱷᱟᱱᱵᱟᱫᱽ ᱦᱚᱱᱚᱛ]] ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱫᱷᱟᱱᱵᱟᱫᱽ ᱥᱟᱫᱟᱨ ᱡᱚᱜᱚ ᱠᱷᱚᱸᱰ ᱨᱮ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱯᱩᱲᱥᱤ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|date=2017-03-09|title=Living above a century-old coal fire, Jharia residents pay the price for India’s mining ambitions|url=https://news.mongabay.com/2017/03/living-above-a-century-old-coal-fire-jharia-residents-pay-the-price-for-indias-mining-ambitions/|access-date=2020-08-02|website=Mongabay Environmental News|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite book|last=Pai|first=Sandeep|url=https://books.google.com.uy/books?id=-iMZtQEACAAJ&dq=Total+Transition:+The+Human+Side+of+the+Renewable+Energy+Revolution&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjrl9mK1vzqAhXCHbkGHbE-DU4Q6AEwAHoECAIQAg|title=Total Transition: The Human Side of the Renewable Energy Revolution|last2=Carr-Wilson|first2=Savannah|date=2018|publisher=Rocky Mountain Books|isbn=978-1-77160-248-8|language=en}}</ref> 

